      "title": "About \u2014 BrainDead",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# Pixal3D \u2014 Image \u2192 Textured 3D\n\nSingle image \u2192 3D mesh with **CuMesh simplify** + full **PBR texture bake**.\n\n**Flow:** Load Image \u2192 Pixal3D Preprocess (auto MoGe FOV) \u2192 Pixal3D Image-to-3D \u2192 **CuMesh Simplify** \u2192 **OVoxel Texture Bake** \u2192 textured mesh + diffuse/normal/metallic/roughness \u2192 Export GLB + Preview 3D.\n\nPixal3D weights (~10GB) auto-download on first run. ~16GB VRAM.\n\n---\n**BrainDeadGuild** \u2014 created by **BizaNator**\n[BrainDeadGuild.com](https://BrainDeadGuild.com) \u00b7 [BrainDead.TV](https://BrainDead.TV) \u00b7 [GitHub](https://github.com/BizaNator/ComfyUI-BrainDead) \u00b7 [Discord](https://braindeadguild.com/discord)"
      ]
    }
